{"tid":2408582,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"Galneryus算唔算技術最頂尖既metal band？","createTime":"2021-02-15T05:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T14:10:03.000Z","uid":83340,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2a5fdd057a62139ec46ed830093b2152cdf773","tid":2408582,"uid":83340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PcxOgUbPF44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPcxOgUbPF44&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=1a2ad7b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PcxOgUbPF44</a><br />\n<br />\n8:06 <br />\nSyu支結他solo可以唔洗望一路fing一路彈，仲要無彈錯<br />\nSho主唱係當年日本男高音小野正利，依家已經53歲，但仲keep住副歌下下F5爆住咁唱<br />\nTaka低音bass勁低調，但原來又係超級高手"},{"pid":"3be1d0f0136aeccb3b6a9c09b2f6c0792dfe710e","tid":2408582,"uid":83340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:40:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3Uf_wAUHjqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3Uf_wAUHjqs&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=28ad69b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3Uf_wAUHjqs</a><br />\n<br />\n比較近期既live，F5高音既音色因為50歲聲音退化已經不復往年，但小野san仍然好努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa6d12712a0b968059051b259a76a4136cd656e","tid":2408582,"uid":83340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"仲有就係鼓手，Fumiya離團真係好可惜，佢既力度音色技術又係日本數一數二，依家入團既後生仔LEA屬於新人，街機打鼓遊戲GITADORA頂尖玩家，又係一隻怪物"},{"pid":"f3b8bdcdb1811d8e6869ce1fa97b83893a37d55a","tid":2408582,"uid":59363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"但係SHO寫果啲英文詞成舊屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c067b3be3578aea7991030af4e4e7ac1134fca","tid":2408582,"uid":76610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"一隊我喜愛嘅Band，成員係有實力，Syu就直情唔洗講，但感覺成隊band都係圍住Syu轉，開始d歌嚟嚟去去都係差唔多，係近期stream live首新歌幾正。Fumiya時期其實d歌都咗好多鼓位聽，我幾鍾意，離隊真係幾可惜。 <br />\n<br />\n都好希望下隻album可以加多d其他成員嘅元素入去，好似the Follower taka嘅bass solo，呢d位幾正。 另外近三隻album故事連貫性都幾特別。"},{"pid":"d7c71bd81800d44974c92420356f6fa865e486bb","tid":2408582,"uid":7444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:00:18.000Z","msg":"真係聽左7~8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係香港都搞過一次live 但都好似冇咩人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea878c839c520a95e8413ebe9a0e5ca677544ced","tid":2408582,"uid":371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"你當prog嗰班死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b63314634a9bcdb6252dacd921abf25267cf62","tid":2408582,"uid":371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"我都係鍾意yama b嗰陣嘅galneryus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736051e5410a68a14ea49c91d6e5cc47ed9ef5f9","tid":2408582,"uid":71983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:32:14.000Z","msg":"黎緊出新碟，希望唔好同之前個幾隻碟曲風咁似啦，見Syu用新整pedal錄歌都幾期待<br />\n好想有首Angel of Salvation咁既經典再出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小野唱live冇以前咁穩，聽碟就同以前冇分別咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有朝一日離團有咩人頂到vocal個位<br />\n<br />\nBtw 依家聽Unlucky Morpheus多，依隊真係越黎越正<br />\nFumiya唔留番係Galneryus 有d可惜"},{"pid":"1fdc5848e348846d10e781cb8d0d846f16e0bc99","tid":2408582,"uid":83340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3b8bdcdb1811d8e6869ce1fa97b83893a37d55a","tid":2408582,"uid":59363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"但係S